  "F(x) = integral of (4 cos(x) - 3 sin(x)) dx = 4 sin(x) + 3 cos(x) + C. F(0) = 0 + 3 + C = 5, so C = 2. F(x) = 4 sin(x) + 3 cos(x) + 2.": "F(x) = (4 os(x) - 3 sin(x)) dx = 4 sin(x) + 3 sc(x) + C. F(0) = 0 + 3 + C = 5, 所以 C = 2. F(x) = 4 sin(x) + 3 sc(x) + 2。",
  "What is the integral of x^(2/3) dx?": "x(2/3) dx 的有机组成部分是什么?",
