  "3 ln|2x + 1| + C": "3 In2x + 1+ C",
  "Let u = 2x + 1, du = 2 dx. Integral = (3/2) integral of du/u = (3/2) ln|u| + C = (3/2) ln|2x + 1| + C.": "Letu = 2x + 1, du = 2 dx. Integral = (3/2) du/u = (3/2) Inu + C = (3/2) In2x + 1 + C。",
  "Evaluate the integral of 4x / (x^2 + 9) dx.": "评估 4x / (x% 2 + 9) dx 的构成。",
  "4/(x^2 + 9) + C": "4/(x%2+9)+C+4/(x%2+9)+C",
