  "2 ln(x^2 + 9) + C": "2 内(x%2+9) + C",
  "2 arctan(x/3) + C": "2arctan(x/3)+C",
  "Let u = x^2 + 9, du = 2x dx. Integral = 4 * (1/2) integral of du/u = 2 ln|u| + C = 2 ln(x^2 + 9) + C. Absolute value is unnecessary since x^2 + 9 > 0 always.": "Letu = x%2 + 9, du = 2x dx. Inteminated = 4 * (1/2) du/u = 2 Inu + C = 2 In(x%2 + 9) + C. 绝对值是不必要的,因为 x%2 + 9 > 0 总是 。",
  "What is the integral of (x^3 + 1)/x dx?": "什么是(xx3+1)/x dx的有机组成部分?",
  "x^3/3 + ln|x| + C": "x% 3/3 + Inx + C",
