  "3x^2 + 1/x + C": "3x%2 + 1/x + C",
  "Divide: (x^3 + 1)/x = x^2 + 1/x. Integral of x^2 = x^3/3 and integral of 1/x = ln|x|. Total: x^3/3 + ln|x| + C.": "除法:(x%3+1)/x=x%2+1/x。x%2=x%3/3综合值和1/x=IN%x=IN%3/3综合值。总计:x%3/3+IN%x+C。",
  "Evaluate the integral of 5 cos(x/2) dx.": "评价 5 cs (x/2) dx 的构成。",
