  "An athlete's speed during a race is v(t) = 8 - 0.4t m/s. If the race is 100 meters, at what time does the athlete finish?": "运动员在比赛中的速度是 v(t) = 8 - 0.4t m/s。 如果比赛是100米,运动员何时结束?",
