  "A bacteria culture has growth rate N'(t) = 300e^(0.2t) bacteria per hour. Starting with 1000 bacteria, how many are there after 5 hours?": "细菌文化的生长速度N'(t)=每小时300e(0.2t)细菌。从1000种细菌开始,5小时后有多少细菌?",
