  "A spring system has velocity v(t) = 5 sin(2t) cm/s with initial position x(0) = 3 cm. Find the position function and the amplitude of oscillation from the rest position.": "弹簧系统具有速度 v(t) = 5 sin(2t) cm/s, 初始位置 x(0) = 3 cm。 查找位置函数和从休息位置振荡的振幅 。",
