  "A toy rocket launches with acceleration a(t) = 40 - 10t m/s^2 from rest at ground level. Find the maximum height the rocket reaches before falling back.": "a(t) = 40 - 10t m/s2,从地面休息处发射加速度a(t) = 40 - 10t m/s2的玩具火箭。在返回前找到火箭到达的最大高度。",
